4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for beginners aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The 16-week program features three live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 students. Participants will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, while learning about cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The course emphasizes risk management and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. The program is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop